Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How long you gonna stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...! After the AC\Nstopped working at my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...I really thought I was gonna die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's broken...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't rest during the entire night,\NI need some sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. We need to fix up our\Nnext song in time for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...Fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I already like it as it is though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about it\Nyou aren't happy with?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuh... how do I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes off a bit... generic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Tomo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, I just can't deal with you\Nanymore, "sensei" wannabe. I'm quitting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I'm quitting too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, it's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}9: THE CRESCENT MOON RISES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You said earlier that something\Nfelt off with her music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so. Better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignoring her food as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...You're gonna die at this rate, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A salesman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}WATER TROUBLE? CALL US ON THE DOUBLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the mailbox is broken, can you go check?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello, it's me, Nina!\N- Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, I haven't even\Nsaid anything yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can feel the AC...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't steal others' air without permission!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be a hoarder~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you neighbor complaint magnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one screaming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop ringing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've freshened up,\Ngo home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're evicting me??
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The AC won't be fixed until next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't Momoka-san's place have an AC?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but she works night shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it just me or...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...should we raise the AC?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\s1}Power{\s0} (DO NOT TOUCH)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you, you can't beat this cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pathetic AC could never.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pathetic??{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A little push and it gave up entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the remote said "DO NOT TOUCH"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Long story short,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of our ACs have sadly passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be most honored if you\Ncould host us in your humble abode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for an hour!! I'M BEGGING YOU!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all her fault, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine... just for an hour thooOOOOAAAHH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's Tomo-chan's pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It hates the heat too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you could let that in?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}POWERFUL!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your apartment's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These girls, I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She said since she works close by she's dropping by later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Subaru: The other three said they broke their ACs,\Nso they just occupied my apartment ._.\NYou wanna come too, Momoka-san? \NMomoka: I'm working near the ShinPrince Hotel,\NI'll be done in 30 mins so I'll drop by later\NSubaru: ROGER THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then let's eat together while we're at it~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Momoka: WEY, WEY, LET'S GET SMASHED
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did we agree on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to "just one hour"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh damn, the last train's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You were planning this all along, you devious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on chill out, I brought cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You DID plan this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think about it, we've never\Ndone something like this together~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So just the four of us for now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also got Monopoly\Nif you want! Maybe Risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna sleep in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you {\i1}not{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't your fault, Nina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk with her a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to sleep early?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of you are enough\Nto play cards or whatever else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got something to say, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Something? I should be asking the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\i1}Loser pays for dinner!!\NRUPA: 100 POINTS / NINA: 2 POINTS / SUBARU: 10 POINTS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina being Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything! It's all the AC's fault!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've just dealt with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried killing time in a conbini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried chilling at a bench for an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But being out when you're\Nbroke is just TOO boring!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She end up saying anything about the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing specific...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I could swear she didn't\Nvibe with it though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll taste bad otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you gonna do if my grandma finds out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll drink them all by tomorro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Tomo-chan's pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, she doesn't bite... or is venomous, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,SNAKEEEEEE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't waste it!\N- AAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHHHHH!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind not locking yourself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get rid of it, quick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san is scared of snakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's buried herself in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's a snake! A SNAKE!!\NHow can you be so calm??
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pfft, not really?\N- How am I the weird one here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way all four of you are okay with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to get to know her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san! Isn't that a snake behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,(Just a hairdryer)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she let... go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,BEGONEEEEE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- NICE PITCH!\N- Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, Momoka-san!\N- Get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you break something,\NI'm the one who has to pay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we left the snake with Tomo-chan, so just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, if you break something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not risking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop acting like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're gonna brea--\N- Nina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs96}I'M GONNA KILL YOU ALL!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You also like hiding away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Never come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's so hot...\N- WHOSE FAULT IS IT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a merry band.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry HOW?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, back to work I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And keep that snake away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, where's Snake-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru agreed to let her stay, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God, I wish I was a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we're going back home, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to check up on our apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I even bother seeing \Nyour face if we don't have practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuh, Momoka-san said it was important\Nto meet even outside of practice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're free, do you want to see me practicing guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go grab my guitar real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An acoustic guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Mine-san, the key is to practice regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old guitar, but a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The second string is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you've been studying \Npiano since you were little, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it. \NAnyone could tell something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, guitars are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already starting to get calluses \Non my fingers from practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a bit messy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best you can do for now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you think? I bet people\Nare gonna love this at our concert!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've gotten so good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we had another guitarist,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could really heat things up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Denied.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And performing like this in front\Nof an audience? Are you joking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...mo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Rupa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not qualified enough to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I look like a guitar expert to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are in music theory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... it sounds good enough for a hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...For a hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think I could play on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm! You see, when I saw DD playing live I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That I want to get a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to keep relying on Momoka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stand alongside her instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, alongside everyone too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me know if there's anything I should improve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you keep fooling around like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're never gonna get anywhere!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many times do I gotta tell you, take this seriou--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get that stick out of your ass already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not all of us get the luxury\Nto be taught piano since childhood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't do this anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Wait...\N{\i0}- {\i1}You shut your mouth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried talking to her yesterday too, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cooled down a bit, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, it's not all bad to live without AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting to feel the changing weather on your skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\i1}Nina: I'll wait in the park in front of the apartment\NRupa: Sure thing~\NNina: THANK YOU FOR TODAY\N{\i1}Nina: It's still boiling in here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-san seemed very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bold of you to show your face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I've got a little problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I mean it! It's not about the AC!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You swear?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some serious advice \Nregarding the future of our band.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'll definitely pay you back (in 36 payments) - Iseri Nina{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Tomo say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That if I keep fooling around like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not gonna get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's not the type to mince words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so, that's good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you think, Subaru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to agree with Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I practiced \Nenough to give it a shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would need at least a year \Nor two to get good enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if you want to play it professionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you seem to be able to wing it so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I asked Tomo, I'm sure she'd have a whole\Ngrocery list of things to say about my playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's never said anything, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because unlike you,\NI've never asked her for feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo's a pretty shy person, all and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she doesn't like being left out,\Nshe always keeps herself at a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't approach you on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you try to approach her instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,RAWR!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You look just like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be like this too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cleaned out the terrarium,\Nso you can take her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a problem she hasn't eaten anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted some feedback from Subaru-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ouch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't be too big of a deal on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Her old band quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When she came to Tokyo, she recruited members online,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And formed a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... is that when the two of you met?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Alongside another guitarist and drum player.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We said we were gonna go pro, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. A common story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that common?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to say "You're just not working hard enough"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're someone successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that were true,\Neveryone would have an equal chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tomo-chan knows this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's always harping \Nabout this and that never being enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she assumed that all of us \Nwere just as serious about making it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She just kept becoming more \Nand more demanding with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sounds like her alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet you stood by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Tomo-chan said she wanted to go solo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A guarantor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to contact my parents again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promise I won't bother you, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So she came to live with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We started our duo {\i1}Beni Shoga{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And even got an offer to go pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But to get this far, she's had to \Nbutt heads with a lot of people, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel she's become scared to speak her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like even her own feelings aren't good enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of my guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm good enough to play on stage together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's finally eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how careful and timid you can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get anywhere if you just freeze up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tomo-chan. Won't you join me for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't cooled one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From tomorrow, we're back to practice again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping it doesn't rain though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I know I wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm saying it's not enough,\Nit's because it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's just not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you lie to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's what Nina wanted to hear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to play on stage with Momoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why she asked {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she wants to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone always says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm serious!" "I want to improve!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But they really just want to be complimented!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They just want to be showered in comfort...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hear her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,From the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, like that, and like-- fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed my orders, you stupid fingers!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the three of them playing live,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Something became crystal clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These girls... they're serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't care about "can'ts" or "enoughs",
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When on stage, they're just their real selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you've been looking for... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs96}YOU FUCKING SUCK!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I promise I'll become better!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You really suck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... something's really bugging me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think as it is now, this song is just too boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.17,0:23:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}NEXT: "WANDERVOGEL"{\i0}
